{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"onload","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/FileReader/load_event","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Das onload Event wird ausgelöst, wenn der Inhalt von&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsArrayBuffer\">readAsArrayBuffer</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsBinaryString\">readAsBinaryString</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsDataURL\">readAsDataURL</a> or <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsText\">readAsText</a> verfügbar ist.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js; line-numbers  language-js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Callback von einem &lt;input type=\"file\" onchange=\"onChange(event)\"&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">onChange</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> file <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>files<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> reader <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FileReader</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  reader<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onload</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Hier wird der Text der Datei ausgegeben</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>result<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  reader<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">readAsText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>file<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Beispiel","id":"beispiel"}],"summary":"Das onload Event wird ausgelöst, wenn der Inhalt von readAsArrayBuffer, readAsBinaryString, readAsDataURL or readAsText verfügbar ist.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"FileReader: load event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"FileReader.onload","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"FileReader: load イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"FileReader.onload","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"FileReader: load event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/filereader/load_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/filereader/load_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechno